info.author: Megan Hofmann
info.name: knit-script
info.summary: Knit Script is a domain specific programming language for writing v-bed knitting machine instructions. The language is loosely based on conventions from Python 3 but includes support for controlling a knitting machine. The code is interpreted into knitout which can then be processed into instructions for different types of knitting machines.
